## Theme System

Two themes toggled via `useTheme` hook. CSS variables in `src/styles/index.css`.

| Context       | Dark (default)        | Light                 |
|---------------|-----------------------|-----------------------|
| Background    | Rich dark brown       | Clean white           |
| Primary       | Electric gold/green   | Forest green          |
| Secondary     | Violet/purple         | Teal                  |
| Warm accent   | Muted rose            | Honeyed amber         |
| Text          | Off-white creme       | Near-black            |

